title: VA-DJ EddieD Progressive Mix Shows March  September 2014
description:
Progressive / Trance / House Mix Shows from March thru Current-September 2014.  

Some months contain two mixed shows - dependent on month.  

Torrent includes track lists for all mp3 files and cover art is embedded in the mp3 files.  

All mp3 files encoded at 320kbps / 48,0000hz  

Also contains three additional exclusive mixes of Dr. Alban's Sing Hallelujah, Boy George Loverush UK's You're Not the One (#1 Club hit), and a special 13 minute mix of Zedd's hits called the Zeddamix (the accompanying video is also included in torrent).
